race.comment: TAKE ME TO CHURCH (1) resumes for a new stable and looks primed after a sharp jump-out win. Scored over this trip on debut and gets Crowther. Expect him to settle back and launch late. HIDDEN WITNESS (8) didn't fire last start but has prior form that stacks up. Freshened and reunites with Opperman. Can bounce back. THE MARINER (2) showed speed and grit to win at Avoca. Well placed again and can give another bold sight. PRIVATE JET (3) returns after six months and won fresh last prep. Keep safe.
